title: Two Whats?! And A Wow! - No Bones About It
description:
Why are Mindy and Guy Raz conducting an archaeological dig in Mindy's closet?! And what will they uncover about ancient animals?! We've got the questions AND answers in this prehistoric round of Two Whats?! And A Wow! It's up to you to find the WOWs from the WHATs about prehistoric creatures!
